events.name: 売春島の幽霊：安宿の受付嬢

parameters:
Inn Receptionist: It's a strange job, but once you get used
to it, it's quite interesting.

Inn Receptionist: What's up? I didn't receive any
notification about a prostitute coming.
Thief Nora: I have a question about a child's ghost...

Inn Receptionist: It's been a topic of gossip for a while
now.
Thief Nora: Is that true!? Can you tell me about it?

Inn Receptionist: There's nothing in this island that
doesn't come with a price. My information doesn't come
cheap, you know. Is that alright with you?

Thief Nora: I-I'll get scolded by the big man at the
reception if I don't solve this... ugh...

Inn Receptionist: Could it be that the client is a right or
left-handed person!?
Thief Nora: ...Yes, the person is left-handed.

Inn Receptionist: Ahaha, that's a masterpiece! So, the
weakness of that annoying man is a ghost, huh!

Inn Receptionist: Try going to the tavern, there might be
something on the mostly unused second floor.

Inn Receptionist: And this is the difference amount to
balance out the value of your information.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

events.name: ID639『黒薔薇の棘』1-4 村娘チップ

parameters: Clea: I came to help at Melena-san's request!

Pirada Pirates Crew Member: I-I'm a lowly pirate, I
apologize!

Queen: You are the shame of the empire! I will teach you the
pleasure of being plundered... Wait, who are you?

Clea: Please lower your weapons. I came here to rescue the
man who is being restrained.
Clea: If you can't hear me, then once more--

Pirada Pirates Crew Member: W-Wait, I don't know who you
are, but hold on! I'm the one who requested her help!

Pirada Pirates Crew Member: What should I say to the
captain? I got caught up in the Pleasure Island and my
return was delayed...

Clea: I understand the situation. Please return to Melena-
san immediately!
Clea (Next, let's look for a tailor)
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Queen: Hehe, actually my favorite hobbies are sewing and
cooking. The ingredients that customers bring me are what
make me the happiest!

events.name: クレア（売春島コス：村娘）
